~ Knuckle Song

@bpm 120
@key F#_major
@loop 2

track
    @instrument sine
    @volume -5
    @pan 1
    @octave 0

    ~ Down melody
    3+2+1+. 6 & 5 . [x3]
    3 . 2 . . . 1 .

    ~ Up melody
    1 2 3 . 5 & 6 . [x3]
    1+. 2+. . . 1+.
end


track
    @instrument triangle
    @octave -1
    @chords

    ~ Down melody
    & & 1 & & & 1 & [x3]
    & & 2 . . . 1 &

    & & 1 & & & 1 & [x3]
    & & 2 . . . 1 &
end